Notes:

OK 1. The email must validated with the following regular expression: \w+@[a-z]+\.[a-z]{2,}

OK 2. The dropdown should have the following options:
   2.1 Standard: chocolate, vanilla, iogurt
   2.2 Fruits: melon, mango, kiwi, strawberry

OK 3. All inputs are mandatory, except the special requests section;

OK 4. The password must have between 6 and 20 characters;

OK 5. The special requests section cannot have more than 100 characters;

OK 6. The 'Waffle cone' option must be disabled;

OK 7. The 'Cup' option should be selected by default;